    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "@zackify thanks for submitting this issue. Indeed the configure is only adding new elements.\r\n\r\n@mthuret What about we cache the previous configure props and create a delta that we would then apply? This mean that when a property is removed we will know it instead of being left in the state it was previously set.\r\n\r\nIn the meantime, @zackify, can you to force the value of `insideBoundingBox` to `''` at step 2?",
